-06-07T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月之後又一個月</blockquote><br />\nDNA去驗仔都係一個星期就有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拖左兩個月明顯搵方法來做手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165e6df89a053925fc08efd0f2a5268975b7b6a1","tid":274004,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆你個街咁份老強嘅DNA報告呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢死左要查但係唔係佢強條女都要查喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強姦係嚴重罪行, 呢單重要係街上隨機 (受害人同疑犯唔識)<br />\n<br />\nDNA 啱定啱先. <br />\n若果唔啱嘅話, 咁即係個犯在逃, 市民好危險.<br />\n<br />\n差佬好快 d 講單強姦案點樣喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b585a7cd9f5d6198202c253e6e03e72b6fde82","tid":274004,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"留名睇&quot;死於不幸&quot;，未能証實疑人老強"},{"pid":"c0062a41cfd39ee7158cf343c4dd0f5de5c5d1e4","tid":274004,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"查咩查咁耐"}]}